page.title: 10CHILDREN'S TRAVEL.
page.content: MOST PEOPLE IN 1985 TRAVEL OUT OF THE AREA IN WHICH THEY WERE BORN,ON BUSINESS, TO LOOK FOR WORK,TO VISIT RELATIVES,OR TO GO ON HOLIDAY.THE POPULATION IS THEREFORE PROBABLY MORE FREE MOVING THAN AT ANY OTHER TIME. THE FOLLOWING FORMS OF TRANSPORT WERE USED BY A SAMPLE OF A HUNDRED ELEVEN YEAR OLD CHILDREN DURING THE MONTH OF MAY.
